---DESCRIPTION---
Switch cases must have a comment if they do not have a break
---CONTENTS---
<?php

switch ($expr) {
    case 0:
        echo 'foo';
    case 1:
        echo 'bar';
        // no break
    default:
        echo 'baz';
}

---MESSAGES---
4:5 PSR2.ControlStructures.SwitchDeclaration.TerminatingComment
---
